dev environment, and then you have like all these like, you know, SIP, PAT, whatever you want to

00:43:01.840 --> 00:43:06.479
call it. And they have this thing called, you know, SDLC, like the software development life

00:43:06.479 --> 00:43:10.639
cycle. So what they would do is typically it's like, well, you work with dev data, which is

00:43:10.639 --> 00:43:15.760
non production, like fake data, and then you do that. But what we eventually convinced them is

