that, well, we kind of need a dev, but we need a dev that's with like real data, like essentially

00:43:20.000 --> 00:43:24.639
a sandbox, because working as a data scientist with fake data becomes a little bit difficult,

00:43:24.639 --> 00:43:28.719
right, when you're actually trying to prove results and things. So, so yeah, so the sandbox

00:43:28.719 --> 00:43:33.199
idea of like, you know, it, it looks like a production, it breathes like a production,

00:43:33.199 --> 00:43:38.399
but it's not production. That's something that I think is key for any data science team to be,

00:43:38.399 --> 00:43:43.679
you know, to be useful, right? So that having being able to have the freedom to do that,

00:43:43.679 --> 00:43:47.439
yeah, I fully agree. Yeah, that's a great point. So as long as you can kind of create what you need

